QUERY_TEXT:
with active_contracts as (
  select distinct contract_number
  from SNOWFLAKE.ORGANIZATION_USAGE.CONTRACT_ITEMS
  where (EXPIRATION_DATE is null or EXPIRATION_DATE >= current_date())
  and START_DATE <= current_date()
),
capacity_balances as (
select 
  contract_number, 
  date,
  greatest(coalesce(free_usage_balance, 0), 0) as free_usage_balance,
  greatest(coalesce(capacity_balance, 0), 0) as capacity_balance,
  greatest(coalesce(rollover_balance, 0), 0) as rollover_balance,
  row_number() over (partition by contract_number order by date desc) as row_num,
  currency
from SNOWFLAKE.ORGANIZATION_USAGE.REMAINING_BALANCE_DAILY
where contract_number in (select contract_number from active_contracts)
)
select sum(free_usage_balance + capacity_balance + rollover_balance) as balance, any_value(currency) as currency
from capacity_balances
where row_num = 1;

select query_parameterized_hash
, count(*) as num_queries

, avg(execution_time) as avg_execution_time_ms
, min(execution_time) as min_execution_time_ms
, max(execution_time) as max_execution_time_ms
, median(execution_time) as median_execution_time_ms

, sum(execution_time) as total_execution_time
, max_by(warehouse_name, end_time) as last_used_warehouse
, max_by(warehouse_size, end_time) as last_used_warehouse_size
, max_by(query_id, end_time) as most_recent_query_id
, max_by(query_text, end_time) as most_recent_query_text
, max(end_time) as most_recent_query_end_time

from snowflake.account_usage.query_history

order by sum(case 
    when warehouse_size = 'X-Small' then 1

    else 0 
end 
* case

end) desc
limit 1000;

, max(execution_time) as max_execution_time_ms
, median(execution_time) as median_execution_time_ms

, sum(execution_time) as total_execution_time
, max_by(warehouse_name, end_time) as last_used_warehouse
, max_by(warehouse_size, end_time) as last_used_warehouse_size
, max_by(query_id, end_time) as most_recent_query_id
, max_by(query_text, end_time) as most_recent_query_text
, max(end_time) as most_recent_query_end_time

from snowflake.account_usage.query_history 
where end_time>=TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-15T00:00:00Z') and end_time<TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-23T00:00:00Z') and LENGTH(TRIM(query_text)) > 0
group by all
order by sum(case 
    when warehouse_size = 'X-Small' then 1
    when warehouse_size = 'Small' then 2
    when warehouse_size = 'Medium' then 4
    when warehouse_size = 'Large' then 8
    when warehouse_size = 'X-Large' then 16
    when warehouse_size = '2X-Large' then 32
    when warehouse_size = '3X-Large' then 64
    when warehouse_size = '4X-Large' then 128
    when warehouse_size = '5X-Large' then 256
    when warehouse_size = '6X-Large' then 512
    else 0 
end 
* case 
    when warehouse_type = 'STANDARD' then 1 
    when warehouse_type = 'SNOWPARK-OPTIMIZED' then 1.5 
    else 0
end) desc
limit 1000;

with active_contracts as (
  select distinct contract_number
  from SNOWFLAKE.ORGANIZATION_USAGE.CONTRACT_ITEMS
  where (EXPIRATION_DATE is null or EXPIRATION_DATE >= current_date())
  and START_DATE <= current_date()
),
capacity_balances as (
select 
  contract_number, 
  date,
  greatest(coalesce(free_usage_balance, 0), 0) as free_usage_balance,
  greatest(coalesce(capacity_balance, 0), 0) as capacity_balance,
  greatest(coalesce(rollover_balance, 0), 0) as rollover_balance,
  row_number() over (partition by contract_number order by date desc) as row_num,
  currency
from SNOWFLAKE.ORGANIZATION_USAGE.REMAINING_BALANCE_DAILY
where contract_number in (select contract_number from active_contracts)
)
select sum(free_usage_balance + capacity_balance + rollover_balance) as balance, any_value(currency) as currency
from capacity_balances
where row_num = 1;

select sum(usage_in_currency) as currency_used from SNOWFLAKE.ORGANIZATION_USAGE.USAGE_IN_CURRENCY_DAILY where usage_date < TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-23T00:00:00Z') and usage_date >= TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-15T00:00:00Z') and account_name = 'VT03840';

select warehouse_name, warehouse_id, sum(credits_used) as credits from snowflake.account_usage.warehouse_metering_history where start_time >= TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-15T00:00:00Z') and start_time < TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-23T00:00:00Z') group by 1,2 order by 3 desc limit 1000;

SELECT *
FROM WHO_SITUATION_REPORTS
MATCH_RECOGNIZE (
    PARTITION BY COUNTRY
    ORDER BY DATE
    MEASURES
        MATCH_NUMBER() AS match_num,
        FIRST(DATE) AS start_date,
        LAST(DATE) AS end_date,
        FINAL COUNT(*) AS days_count
    ONE ROW PER MATCH
    AFTER MATCH SKIP PAST LAST ROW
    PATTERN (ST_UP* UP_ROW)
    DEFINE
        UP_ROW AS CASES_NEW > LAG(CASES_NEW) * 1.5
);

SELECT 
    CASE 
       WHEN CHARINDEX('/', RELATIVE_PATH) = 1 THEN RIGHT(RELATIVE_PATH, LEN(RELATIVE_PATH) -1 )
       ELSE RELATIVE_PATH
    END
   as SAFE_RELATIVE_PATH, IFNULL(
            NULLIF(
              SUBSTR(SAFE_RELATIVE_PATH, LENGTH(SAFE_RELATIVE_PATH) + 2 - CHARINDEX('/', REVERSE(SAFE_RELATIVE_PATH))), 
              ''
            ), 
            SAFE_RELATIVE_PATH

select query_parameterized_hash
, count(*) as num_queries

, avg(execution_time) as avg_execution_time_ms
, min(execution_time) as min_execution_time_ms
, max(execution_time) as max_execution_time_ms
, median(execution_time) as median_execution_time_ms

, sum(execution_time) as total_execution_time
, max_by(warehouse_name, end_time) as last_used_warehouse
, max_by(warehouse_size, end_time) as last_used_warehouse_size
, max_by(query_id, end_time) as most_recent_query_id
, max_by(query_text, end_time) as most_recent_query_text
, max(end_time) as most_recent_query_end_time

from snowflake.account_usage.query_history 
where end_time>=TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-18T00:00:00Z') and end_time<TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-26T00:00:00Z') and LENGTH(TRIM(query_text)) > 0
group by all
order by sum(case 
    when warehouse_size = 'X-Small' then 1
    when warehouse_size = 'Small' then 2
    when warehouse_size = 'Medium' then 4
    when warehouse_size = 'Large' then 8
    when warehouse_size = 'X-Large' then 16
    when warehouse_size = '2X-Large' then 32
    when warehouse_size = '3X-Large' then 64
    when warehouse_size = '4X-Large' then 128
    when warehouse_size = '5X-Large' then 256
    when warehouse_size = '6X-Large' then 512
    else 0 
end 
* case 
    when warehouse_type = 'STANDARD' then 1 
    when warehouse_type = 'SNOWPARK-OPTIMIZED' then 1.5 
    else 0
end) desc
limit 1000;

FROM (SELECT COUNTRY_REGION, DATE, AVG(CASES) AS CASES, AVG(DEATHS) AS DEATHS
      FROM ECDC_GLOBAL
      GROUP BY COUNTRY_REGION, DATE) m
WHERE m.CASES > 0;

SHOW OUTGOING LISTING REQUESTS IN DATA EXCHANGE identifier('"SNOWFLAKE_DATA_MARKETPLACE"');
SHOW AVAILABLE LISTINGS  IN DATA EXCHANGE "SNOWFLAKE_DATA_MARKETPLACE"

select sum(usage_in_currency) as currency_used from SNOWFLAKE.ORGANIZATION_USAGE.USAGE_IN_CURRENCY_DAILY where usage_date < TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-26T00:00:00Z') and usage_date >= TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-18T00:00:00Z') and account_name = 'VT03840';

select EFFECTIVE_RATE, DATE from snowflake.organization_usage.rate_sheet_daily where account_name = 'VT03840' and SERVICE_TYPE = 'COMPUTE' and DATE < TO_DATE('2024-01-26T00:00:00Z') and DATE >= TO_DATE('2024-01-18T00:00:00Z') order by DATE desc limit 1;

select database_name, database_id, MAX(AVERAGE_DATABASE_BYTES) as database_bytes from snowflake.account_usage.database_storage_usage_history where usage_date >= '2024-01-18T00:00:00Z' and usage_date < '2024-01-26T00:00:00Z' group by 1,2 order by 3 desc limit 1000;

select warehouse_name, warehouse_id, sum(credits_used) as credits from snowflake.account_usage.warehouse_metering_history where start_time >= TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-18T00:00:00Z') and start_time < TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-26T00:00:00Z') group by 1,2 order by 3 desc limit 1000;

select 'current_period' as time, IFNULL(SUM(credits_used), 0) as credits from snowflake.account_usage.metering_history where start_time >= TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-18T00:00:00Z') and start_time < TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-26T00:00:00Z')

select query_parameterized_hash
, count(*) as num_queries

, avg(execution_time) as avg_execution_time_ms
, min(execution_time) as min_execution_time_ms
, max(execution_time) as max_execution_time_ms
, median(execution_time) as median_execution_time_ms

, sum(execution_time) as total_execution_time
, max_by(warehouse_name, end_time) as last_used_warehouse
, max_by(warehouse_size, end_time) as last_used_warehouse_size
, max_by(query_id, end_time) as most_recent_query_id
, max_by(query_text, end_time) as most_recent_query_text
, max(end_time) as most_recent_query_end_time

from snowflake.account_usage.query_history 
where end_time>=TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-18T00:00:00Z') and end_time<TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-26T00:00:00Z') and LENGTH(TRIM(query_text)) > 0
group by all
order by sum(case 
    when warehouse_size = 'X-Small' then 1
    when warehouse_size = 'Small' then 2
    when warehouse_size = 'Medium' then 4
    when warehouse_size = 'Large' then 8
    when warehouse_size = 'X-Large' then 16
    when warehouse_size = '2X-Large' then 32
    when warehouse_size = '3X-Large' then 64
    when warehouse_size = '4X-Large' then 128
    when warehouse_size = '5X-Large' then 256
    when warehouse_size = '6X-Large' then 512
    else 0 
end 
* case 
    when warehouse_type = 'STANDARD' then 1 
    when warehouse_type = 'SNOWPARK-OPTIMIZED' then 1.5 
    else 0
end) desc
limit 1000;

        w.TOTAL_CASES,
        w.CASES_NEW,
        w.DEATHS,
        w.DEATHS_NEW,
        w.DATE,
        e.POPULATION
    FROM WHO_SITUATION_REPORTS w
    JOIN ECDC_GLOBAL e ON w.COUNTRY = e.COUNTRY_REGION AND w.DATE = e.DATE

WITH CasesWithLag AS (
        SELECT
            w.COUNTRY,
            w.DATE,
            w.CASES_NEW,
            LAG(w.CASES_NEW) OVER (PARTITION BY w.COUNTRY ORDER BY w.DATE) AS PREV_DAY_CASES
        FROM WHO_SITUATION_REPORTS w
        JOIN ECDC_GLOBAL e ON w.COUNTRY = e.COUNTRY_REGION AND w.DATE = e.DATE
)
    SELECT
        COUNTRY,
        DATE,
        CASES_NEW
    FROM CasesWithLag
    WHERE CASES_NEW >= 5 * PREV_DAY_CASES

select query_parameterized_hash
, count(*) as num_queries

, avg(execution_time) as avg_execution_time_ms
, min(execution_time) as min_execution_time_ms
, max(execution_time) as max_execution_time_ms
, median(execution_time) as median_execution_time_ms

, sum(execution_time) as total_execution_time
, max_by(warehouse_name, end_time) as last_used_warehouse
, max_by(warehouse_size, end_time) as last_used_warehouse_size
, max_by(query_id, end_time) as most_recent_query_id
, max_by(query_text, end_time) as most_recent_query_text
, max(end_time) as most_recent_query_end_time

from snowflake.account_usage.query_history 
where end_time>=TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-18T00:00:00Z') and end_time<TO_TIMESTAMP_LTZ('2024-01-26T00:00:00Z') and LENGTH(TRIM(query_text)) > 0
group by all
order by sum(case 
    when warehouse_size = 'X-Small' then 1
    when warehouse_size = 'Small' then 2
    when warehouse_size = 'Medium' then 4
    when warehouse_size = 'Large' then 8
    when warehouse_size = 'X-Large' then 16
    when warehouse_size = '2X-Large' then 32
    when warehouse_size = '3X-Large' then 64
    when warehouse_size = '4X-Large' then 128
    when warehouse_size = '5X-Large' then 256
    when warehouse_size = '6X-Large' then 512
    else 0 
end 
* case 
    when warehouse_type = 'STANDARD' then 1 
    when warehouse_type = 'SNOWPARK-OPTIMIZED' then 1.5 
    else 0
end) desc
limit 1000;

            LAG(w.CASES_NEW) OVER (PARTITION BY w.COUNTRY ORDER BY w.DATE) AS PREV_DAY_CASES
        FROM WHO_SITUATION_REPORTS w
        JOIN ECDC_GLOBAL e ON w.COUNTRY = e.COUNTRY_REGION AND w.DATE = e.DATE
)
    SELECT
        COUNTRY,
        DATE,
        CASES_NEW
    FROM CasesWithLag
    WHERE CASES_NEW >= 10 * PREV_DAY_CASES
